{"tid":579752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國復辟帝制 香江第一才子諷習下一步將訪求...","createTime":"2018-03-04T01:27:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T03:23:53.000Z","uid":35790,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"62a6e98d98c277c4e37426368b51b6d89113fd98","tid":579752,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:27:17.000Z","msg":"中國復辟帝制 香江第一才子諷習下一步將訪求...<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國人大正在召開，很可能修憲，取消國家主席的任期制，引發外界復辟帝制的高度評論，擁香江第一才子之稱的陶傑，在一篇評論中認為，中國在經過百年「探索」之後，竟然復辟帝制，而在沒人「敢」當接班人的情況下，習近平的下一步，「即是海外訪求長生不老藥矣」。<br />\n<br />\n陶傑在香港《蘋果日報》的一篇文章中指出，「中國強人專權的帝制，也首先要肯定世襲」，毛澤東做皇帝，也早就意識到接班人的問題，先是培養毛岸英，後又指定劉少奇，最後是林彪。<br />\n<br />\n陶傑認為，「但現在的中共，卻沒有副總書記之職。看見孫政才這般下場，即使開一個新的副總書記位，哪個敢坐上去的，哪個就是現成的野心家。『帝制』不要緊，不可以有帝而無制，無制即無繼嗣，下一步即是海外訪求長生不老藥矣。」<br />\n<br />\n陶傑忍不住指出，改革回歸帝制，就差接班人問題，其他什麼「中國人在世上丟盡臉」之類的流言，就不必理會了，反正丟臉的事很多，像是中國留學生大鬧機艙、抄襲作弊等民族羞辱的丟臉天天大把，也不在乎多這一件了。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"},{"pid":"2665ac0635ababe565b8147772065fa0e7b2a6e8","tid":579752,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a7907fda4b22a33c42465f565959167dd28f80c","tid":579752,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:32:03.000Z","msg":"長生不老藥美國有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8db2a16e5aa0da9e2deab98e4b96d57e9551f2a","tid":579752,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a7907fda4b22a33c42465f565959167dd28f80c","tid":579752,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:32:03.000Z","msg":"長生不老藥美國有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:34:48.000Z","msg":"聽聞李超人研發緊"},{"pid":"18c1b91398cb69d4368819bab891c006f80cd544","tid":579752,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:37:03.000Z","msg":"換頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f5ef60b2d8c0394607b4e0c71ff99f59a1a7ed3","tid":579752,"uid":47674,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:39:25.000Z","msg":"反正丟臉的事很多<br />\n也不在乎多這一件了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b01fbb072748845cde32006dd47b812f4b9388","tid":579752,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f5ef60b2d8c0394607b4e0c71ff99f59a1a7ed3","tid":579752,"uid":47674,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:39:25.000Z","msg":"反正丟臉的事很多<br />\n也不在乎多這一件了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a43db09488f1217964c3d448ffaf985e2f674da","tid":579752,"uid":14706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:40:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">其他什麼「中國人在世上丟盡臉」之類的流言，就不必理會了，反正丟臉的事很多，像是中國留學生大鬧機艙、抄襲作弊等民族羞辱的丟臉天天大把，也不在乎多這一件了。</span><br />\n<br />\n真係人無恥則天下無敵"},{"pid":"8b24bba5fd876ba0851275bd26d208edcced5253","tid":579752,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48b01fbb072748845cde32006dd47b812f4b9388","tid":579752,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f5ef60b2d8c0394607b4e0c71ff99f59a1a7ed3","tid":579752,"uid":47674,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:39:25.000Z","msg":"反正丟臉的事很多<br />\n也不在乎多這一件了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T01:46:57.000Z","ms